PrecisAmendment to the INCOME TAX REGULATIONS establishing a list of companies that will be considered to be "prescribed insurers" providing that eligibility for the exemption from tax will be determined without reference to the gross premium income of affiliated insurers, thus permitting them to continue to compete and maintain their historic market position in the insurance of risks of farmers and fishermen.

precis:
Amendment to the INCOME TAX REGULATIONS establishing a list of companies
that will be considered to be "prescribed insurers" providing that
eligibility for the exemption from tax will be determined without
reference to the gross premium income of affiliated insurers, thus
permitting them to continue to compete and maintain their historic market
position in the insurance of risks of farmers and fishermen.
